Ask HN: Does Notion sometimes lose notes?
text:
Somehow the entire task list is gone from the Android app, and the webpage version cannot open at all (spinning after clicking login). Did any experience anything similar?

Anyway I probably will never use anything that doesn't store things locally again. Can anyone recommend a solution that covers both Android and windows and can sync between each other when both are in the same wifi? Thanks! Or maybe should it be my Android learning project?

Show HN: Giving away my Notion brand guidelines template
text:
I've created my first Notion template to make it easier for anyone to organize their brand guidelines.

Instead of spending lots of time and money on a brand management service (such as Frontify), you can actually do everything in Notion.

All I'm looking for is your feedback to improve the template before it's officially released.

Have a great weekend!
